Question No: 5

Write a Java (JDBC) program to connect with the MySQL database and 
print the book details after deleting a particular book from the database.


Use below Database Credentials
Driver Class    : com.mysql.jdbc.Driver
Default DB URL : jdbc:mysql://localhost/ri_db
Username     : test
Password      : test123

Note: The table is already created, and a set of book details are inserted.

Id	    name		          author
1	      Alchemist	        Paulo Coelho
2	      Divergent	        Veronica
3 	    The red		        Stendhal
4	      Pride and 	      Jane Austen
	      Prejudice	
5	      Politics	        Aristotle
6	      Power Politics	  Arundati Roy
7	      Anand Math	      Bankim Chandra Chatterjee
8	      My Truth	        Indira Gandhi


Input format
The input consists of the book name.

Output format
The output prints the table after deleting the particular book.

Input 1					    Output 1
Alchemist				    2 Divergent Veronica
					          3 The red Stendhal
					          4 Pride and Prejudice Jane Austen
					          5 Politics Aristotle
					          6 Power Politics Arundati Roy
					          7 Anand Math Bankim Chandra Chatterjee
					          8 My Truth Indira Gandhi
